  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the integration of LLMs in an API allows efficient preprompting that allows the provision of an example solution.",
    "In this way, LLMs are aware of the correct solution and can guide the learner towards it without hallucination [15].",
    "Ms offer a range of options for learners, as recent research shows.",
    "Fauzi and colleagues discuss the role of GPT in stimulating contextual learning strategies, thereby enhancing metacognitive abilities [18].",
    "This aspect is important for the development of self-regulated learning skills."
  ]
